.SH STANDARDS
POSIX.1-2001, POSIX.1-2008, C89, C99, SVr4, 4.3BSD.
The functions
.BR lldiv ()
and
.BR imaxdiv ()
were added in C99.
.SH EXAMPLES
After
.PP
.in +4n
.EX
div_t q = div(\-5, 3);
.EE
.in
.PP
the values \fIq.quot\fP and \fIq.rem\fP are \-1 and \-2, respectively.
